{"tid":1105973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東亞銀行擺烏龍　向市民退款加回贈$5,300變53萬","createTime":"2019-04-14T09:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T17:04:33.000Z","uid":20933,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3d4c9f2b1345d3910ef1983aa6ee55da6aadacd6","tid":1105973,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T09:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190414/large/1555233470_e771.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190414%2Flarge%2F1555233470_e771.jpg&h=0897fbf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東亞銀行（023）疑似系統出錯，多位讀者爆料指，近日獲退回的手續費由5千元變50萬元，本來僅獲300元現金回贈，卻變成回贈3萬元。本報向東亞查詢，該行指正了解情況。<br />\n<br />\n讀者張先生指，早前參與東亞銀行網上結餘轉戶及網上繳稅計劃，只要交易金額滿10萬元或以上，即可獲現金回贈300元，以及退回手續費5,000元，至今日查看戶口，驚覺銀行存入共53萬元！<br />\n<br />\n另有讀者Alex表示，他原先同樣獲退回5000元手續費及300元現金回贈，惟發現數日前東亞銀行向其信用卡戶口分別存入50萬元及3萬元，他續指已與銀行聯絡，「現時已經解決咗，將有關交易取消了，估計是回贈多咗，即係打少咗個點咁囉」。<br />\n<br />\n他又透露，有同屬東亞特選客戶的友人亦受影響，共通點是兩人均參與「網上結餘轉戶及網上繳稅計劃」，「唔知係個別事件，抑或是系統出錯啦」。"},{"pid":"e999f992023ff1a2680f8312ce13009b41c41c5d","tid":1105973,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T09:42:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190414/59487580\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190414%2F59487580&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8mLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=ef661689\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190414%2F59487580&h=8c055033\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190414/59487580</a>"},{"pid":"a2426278fa53219df131a233f2ab81ca368ac98d","tid":1105973,"uid":42250,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T09:43:08.000Z","msg":"蠢老鼠"},{"pid":"f3ac466477f14247f22a447a85c2554566104a45","t